a.n: Valor Bare Knuckle Boxing, New Town, USA 22.09.2019

p.k: Ken Shamrock, UFC síň slávy a "Nejnebezpečnější muž na světě" spouští nové promo VALOR! Bare Knuckle Boxing si lidem zalíbilo po celém světě a VALOR
p.d: Ken Shamrock, UFC Hall of Fame and the “World’s Most Dangerous Man” is launching the new Bare Knuckle Boxing promotion VALOR! Bare Knuckle Boxing is currently taking the world by a storm and VALOR, with legend Ken Shamrock as front man, will create great impact in the scene and bring thrilling, top level events. The VALOR shows will be held in a pit. This together the fighters’ hands only wrapped up brings the audiences the most pure and exciting form of fighting.
